Sex video official sentenced 13 years in jail 
2013-06-28 04:04:24 GMT
A former official embroiled in a sex video scandal was sentenced to 13 years in jail for bribery on Friday morning in southwest China's Chongqing Municipality.Lei Zhengfu, former secretary of Chongqing's Beibei District Committee of the Communist Party of China, was also fined 300,000 yuan (48,554 U.S. dollars), according to a Chongqing No. 1 Intermediate People's Court ruling.Lei said he would consider whether or not to appeal after the trial.The 55-year-old was found to have appeared in a sex video that was posted online in November.
